OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778872268
OL,3,CJosh Simons: Electing Andy Burnham is
OL,4,C'best way to improve constituents
OL,5,Clives'
OL,7,FThe MP standing down in the Makerfield
OL,8,Fconstituency to make way for Andy
OL,9,FBurnham says electing him is 'the best
OL,10,Fway to improve constituents lives'.
OL,12,FJosh Simons defended his actions,
OL,13,Fsaying the people of Makerfield will
OL,14,Fhave the opportunity to 'change the
OL,15,Ftrajectory of the country'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
