FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778872268
OL,3,CJosh Simons: Electing Andy Burnham is
OL,4,C'best way to improve constituents
OL,5,Clives'
OL,7,FHe said: "I'm not passing anything to
OL,8,Fanyone, it's a by-election. That means
OL,9,Fthat the people of Makerfield, in my
OL,10,Fconstituency, they get to decide not
OL,11,Fjust who is their local MP, but they
OL,12,Fare going to have a choice that
OL,13,Fchanges the trajectory of the country,
OL,14,Ffrankly."
OL,16,FJosh Simons MP announced he would
OL,17,Fstand down, so that Andy Burnham could
OL,18,Ffight to re-enter Parliament.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
