OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778872268
OL,3,CJosh Simons: Electing Andy Burnham is
OL,4,C'best way to improve constituents
OL,5,Clives'
OL,7,FMr Simons said: "They can choose to
OL,8,Felect Andy Burnham, who has basically
OL,9,Fpromised to go and change the Labour
OL,10,FParty and change Westminster.
OL,12,F"If they give him that mandate or they
OL,13,Fcan choose not to, and that will
OL,14,Fchange the fate of the Labour Party
OL,15,Facross the North and and the Midlands.
OL,16,FAnd I think giving my constituents
OL,17,Fthat choice is really, really
OL,18,Fimportant for changing what happens
OL,19,Fnext."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
