PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778872268
OL,3,CJosh Simons: Electing Andy Burnham is
OL,4,C'best way to improve constituents
OL,5,Clives'
OL,7,FThe Mayor of Greater Manchester has
OL,8,Flong been seen as a potential rival to
OL,9,FSir Keir Starmer, but he has been
OL,10,Funable to officially challenge the
OL,11,FPrime Minister because he is not a
OL,12,Fsitting MP.
OL,14,FAndy Burnham previously attempted to
OL,15,Fstand as the Labour candidate in the
OL,16,FGorton and Denton by-election, but his
OL,17,Fbid was blocked by Labour's National
OL,18,FExecutive Committee.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
