FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778872268
OL,3,CJosh Simons: Electing Andy Burnham is
OL,4,C'best way to improve constituents
OL,5,Clives'
OL,7,FWhen asked how Mr Simons felt about
OL,8,Fstepping away from his work in the
OL,9,Fconstituency, he said: "Very often
OL,10,Fwhat I found is the the way they work
OL,11,F(in Westminster) gets in the way of
OL,12,Fgetting them done, even when my party
OL,13,Fis in power.
OL,26,@sD@ApmsD@Ppn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778872268
OL,3,CJosh Simons: Electing Andy Burnham is
OL,4,C'best way to improve constituents
OL,5,Clives'
OL,7,F"And I've said very openly that I
OL,8,Fdon't think my Government, the Labour
OL,9,FGovernment, has the bravery and the
OL,10,Fradicalism and the appetite for really
OL,11,Fchanging things that would be needed
OL,12,Fto move the dial on all of that. And
OL,13,Factually, this moment now, I had a
OL,14,Fchoice, which was my constituency has
OL,15,Fthe potential to choose whether to
OL,16,Fsend Andy Burnham down to Westminster
OL,17,Fto change some of that.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778872268
OL,3,CJosh Simons: Electing Andy Burnham is
OL,4,C'best way to improve constituents
OL,5,Clives'
OL,7,F"And at the end of the day, what I
OL,8,Fconcluded was that is the best way to
OL,9,Fget some of these things done, because
OL,10,Fconstantly MPs like me will be
OL,11,Ffighting against the system in order
OL,12,Fto do these things unless the system
OL,13,Fchanges. And I couldn't say no to
OL,14,Fthat, to that chance in the end."
OL,16,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,17,Four political experts are across all
OL,18,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,19,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
